Before transacting business in this Commonwealth, a foreign limited liability partnership shall file a statement of foreign qualification. The statement shall contain:
The name of the foreign limited liability partnership which satisfies the requirements of KRS 14A.3-010;
The street address of the partnership's chief executive office and, if different, the street address of an office of the partnership in this Commonwealth, if any;
The partnership's registered office and the name of its registered agent at that office, which shall comply with KRS 14A.4-010; and
Its jurisdiction of organization.
